<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="114" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,150,285]" pageId="11" pageNumber="114">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,186,212]" pageId="11" pageNumber="114">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species is named after the 
<typeStatus box="[682,730,187,213]" pageId="11" pageNumber="114">type</typeStatus>
